{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotations:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotations"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of annotation objects to remove. Objects in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"array must conform to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotations"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removing annotation objects dissociates them from the map view entirely,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing them from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"call this method only when you want to hide or delete the given annotations."}]}]}],"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1833","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotations:"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"removeAnnotations:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotations:"}],"role":"symbol","